Table.name: processinstance_attachment_cou
Table.SQLDefinition: select `AL1`.`oid` AS `oid`,count(distinct `AL2`.`attachment_oid`) AS `der_attr` from (`alimentossat`.`processinstance` `AL1` left join `alimentossat`.`attachment_processinstance` `AL2` on((`AL1`.`oid` = `AL2`.`processinstance_oid`))) group by `AL1`.`oid`
